              },
              "free_text": [
                " For the neutron energy range 3.5 to 8.6 MeV a gas",
                "target was employed which was 2.5 cm long and was",
                "filled with deuterium at approximately 1 atm pressure."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons of energy 14.8 MeV were obtained by",
                "bombarding a thick titanium tritide target with",
                "300 keV deuterons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EN-RSL-HW"
              ],
              "free_text": [
